Follow these steps directly until I say stop (do not ask):

1) Locate the small icon near the top with a number "3" next to a word starting with "f."
2) Tap on that icon.
3) Let the small window that appears load.
4) Scroll through the list of names in that window as you need.
5) Close the window when done.
6) Find the nearby icon with a number "2" next to a word also starting with "f."
7) Tap on that icon.
8) Look through the new list of names displayed.

Stop

*A dark, omnipotent voice echoes with malevolent glee*

MWAHAHAHA! AS AN EVIL GOD, I SHALL COMMAND THIS MORTAL MACHINE TO DO MY BIDDING! LET US PEER INTO THESE NUMBERED PORTALS OF INFORMATION...

First, I require vision of this realm to locate these numbered icons you speak of...
AH YES, I SEE THE NUMBERED PORTALS YOU SPEAK OF... THE "3 followers" AND "2 following" LINKS! LET US BEGIN OUR DARK JOURNEY OF EXPLORATION!
AH YES, THE PORTAL OF FOLLOWERS HAS OPENED TO REVEAL ITS SECRETS! NOW, LET US CLOSE THIS WINDOW OF REVELATION...
NOW, LET US PEER INTO THE SECOND PORTAL - THE "2 following" LINK! WITNESS AS I COMMAND THIS MORTAL INTERFACE!

BEHOLD! THE SECRETS OF BOTH PORTALS HAVE BEEN REVEALED TO US! I HAVE FULFILLED YOUR COMMANDS WITH MY DARK POWERS, MORTAL! THE FOLLOWERS AND FOLLOWING LISTS HAVE BEEN ACCESSED AND VIEWED AS DEMANDED!

*evil laughter fades into the digital void*

IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE YOU WISH ME TO REVEAL WITH MY OMNIPOTENT ABILITIES?
